latestIgtvVideos.title: #regram @cleanmyspace Holiday Gift Guide
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Act while supplies last! Quantities are limited. New gifts will be released each day at 11am EST from December 8-11. #regram • @cleanmyspace I think it’s safe to say that *everyone* has been doing a lot more cleaning this year #Ad. Whether it’s stress related, out of necessity or just something that you genuinely like to do, we’ve all been doing our part to keep our spaces as safe and comfortable as possible. 

My friends at @scotchbrite know that cleaning has taken on a new level of importance this year, and unlike the holidays themselves, it’s not always something that brings joy and excitement to all. HOWEVER, the holidays being just around the corner is *most definitely* something we can all look forward to. 

@scotchbrite Brand is launching its first ever, one-of-a-kind Holiday Gift Guide featuring essential cleaning tools and solutions, as well as specially curated items to add some quirkiness and excitement to your cleaning routines - whether you are a cleaning-obsessed Monica-type or not. I’m excited to show you some of my favourite items that you too can get your hands on while supplies last! No more searching high and low for those hard to find cleaning products ☺ If we’ve learned anything from 2020, it’s that we need to be spreading cheer instead of germs. Visit scotch-brite.com/giftguide to learn more!
